typical day, more than ten times the volume of alt.english.usage.  Any
given question posted to AUE is likely to get far more answers than
the same question posted to AEU, and in general you'll also find a
much greater depth of knowledge at AUE.  If your purpose in posting is
to get useful answers to questions about English, I recommend AUE over
AEU.

You could also post the same inquiry simultaneously to both groups.
(Not one post each; a single post with both as addressees.)  This will
get you responses from participants in both.
