The difference is mainly in the feel of the two groups.

AUE has more prolific posters, more in-jokes, and more likelyhood that
a question or post will spin off into digressions on linguistic
history, he relative merits of various language theories, or a
completely off-topic  topic, like manual transmissions in cars. It
also has much more traffic (more posts each day.)

AEU has fewer posters, and more likely that the queston will be
answered by people saying &quot;This is the way I've always heard it used,&quot;
or &quot;No, you want a subjunctive there, so use &lt;foo&gt; instead of &lt;bar&gt;,&quot;
without quoting chapter and verse of 6 different grammar books.
